</div>
<div>
<p>
<date notBefore="1034" notAfter="1038">景祐</date>元年<measure quantity="8" unit="months">
<num value="8">八</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>判太常寺燕肅等上言<pc>：</pc>
